2. py manage.py runserver


Activate the virutal thing?:

1. Change directory first:   cd 'C:\Users\Weird\PycharmProjects\Final Web Environment\venv\Scripts'

2. Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope CurrentUser -ExecutionPolicy Unrestricted

3. activate.bat


Make new app {Tutorial page 2?}

1. py manage.py startapp ~Name Here~



Make Models {Tutorial page 2}:

1. Change models in models.py (Use format similar to tutorial stuff)

2. Run "python manage.py makemigrations" to make migrations for the changes

3. Run "python manage.py migrate" to apply the changes




